Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.81,0:00:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,We have to walk again?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.45,0:00:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.79,0:00:10.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph... We're going to\Nthe northern hideout now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.55,0:00:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, you'll be killed\Nthe moment we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:17.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I only know it through maps...\Nbut is the place really that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.71,0:00:21.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The northern hideout\Nis no ordinary hideout.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.67,0:00:25.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That place...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.31,0:00:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is where human experiments\Nare conducted.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.76,0:00:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,And the unmanageable monsters that\Nresult are kept locked up there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.69,0:00:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,A male...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,No, a female.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.39,0:00:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'll kill a male next, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.65,0:00:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.74,0:00:53.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already begun...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.46,0:01:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Why... Why did you have to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.53,0:01:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's pretty heavy food\Nto have in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.96,0:01:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Sakura, today's our day off.\NHow come you're up so early?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.94,0:01:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already noon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.23,0:01:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, never mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.63,0:01:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just wash up quickly and get dressed.\NI'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.14,0:01:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Is it a date?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.56,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Idiot! Lady Tsunade has summoned us!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.71,0:01:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, aren't you tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.73,0:01:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,How about a short break?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.65,0:01:50.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You're already taking a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.92,0:01:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You are so hopeless!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.65,0:01:56.01,Default,,0,0,0,,It's still far to the northern hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:01:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,My destination is different\Nfrom yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.72,0:02:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,No need to bother with me.\NJust go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.48,0:02:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered that I too have business\Nat the northern hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.48,0:02:08.08,Default,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to take care of that first!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.30,0:02:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Move...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.27,0:02:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll kill you too!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.43,0:02:40.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Stop it, Jugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.56,0:02:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.28,0:02:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.21,0:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're not alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.39,0:03:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You have me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Without you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.36,0:03:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I can never leave this place...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.94,0:03:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.76,0:03:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you follow Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have a goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.35,0:03:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And if I stick with Sasuke,\NI can fulfill that goal.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.48,0:03:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, I should be asking you\Nthe same question... Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what your goals are...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.38,0:03:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,But you want me to join your team\Ndespite knowing about Jugo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I know him a little.\NWe fought each other once.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.34,0:03:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,He had an unusual ability\Nand was quite formidable.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.21,0:04:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But I couldn't figure out what he was thinking,\N and I didn't really like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand {\i1}he{\i0} sought out\NOrochimaru.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.63,0:04:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's got to be crazy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.81,Default,,0,0,0,,According to rumors,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.81,0:04:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Jugo usually has that\Nunusual impulse well under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But when he loses it,\Nhe transforms into a ruthless killer.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.18,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,His personality and appearance\Nchange completely.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, he's a maniac\Nwho loves to kill people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.51,0:04:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,But to Orochimaru,\NJugo's ability was enticing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.67,0:04:36.01,Default,,0,0,0,,He invented an enzyme,\Nbased on Jugo's body fluids,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.01,0:04:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,which induced the same condition\Nin other Shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.18,0:04:42.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys know it too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.73,0:04:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...the Curse Mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.62,0:04:54.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Jugo is the one and only\Noriginal carrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm getting out of here!\N{\i1}I'll kill anyone who tries to stop me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.71,0:05:02.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who's...next?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:37.38,Title,,0,0,0,,{\i1\pos(735.938,587.5)}Jugo of the Northern Hideout\N\N
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.07,0:06:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.23,0:06:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What took you two so long?! Cripes!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Naruto was eating lunch,\Nwhich he calls breakfast...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.12,0:06:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Now now... Tsunade...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Pervy Sage?! You're back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.85,0:06:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been awhile, eh, Naruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.56,0:07:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Aw man! Why didn't you tell me\Nyou were back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,We had a hard time after you left.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.59,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,So I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I got the gist of it, but I understand\Nyou played a big part.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.85,0:07:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,That's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.17,0:07:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I finally got my Collaboration Jutsu\Nto work in sync with the two toads.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.42,0:07:18.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?! You finally did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.89,0:07:21.17,Default,,0,0,0,,How about it?\NWanna see my new Jutsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.17,0:07:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, since I'm here...\NI don't mind if I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.72,0:07:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And naturally, after that,\Nwe'll go eat ramen at Ichiraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:32.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, it'll be my treat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.65,0:07:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,- All right! Let's get going!\N- Let's go! Your new Jutsu, eh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.42,0:07:38.32,Default,,0,0,0,,- I'm looking forward to this...\N- Hey!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.20,0:07:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ow!\N- Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.97,0:07:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Say, can we rest a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.20,0:07:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu! You keep stopping to rest!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.85,0:07:57.28,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost at the hideout!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.28,0:08:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it the sword?\NIs it too heavy for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Then leave it, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell him, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.56,0:08:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.92,0:08:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the guy who's on watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.37,0:08:26.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right... That's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.96,0:08:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He's from the northern hideout.\NHe's still breathing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.17,0:08:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.40,0:08:53.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You're...Sasuke Uchiha...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.40,0:08:55.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Help me...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.50,0:09:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It all started...\N with the rumors that Orochimaru was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.94,0:09:10.72,Default,,0,0,0,,The prisoners went wild...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:12.44,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.03,0:09:18.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear... He died.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.10,0:09:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.59,0:09:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.52,0:09:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,He's already in the\N"Curse Mark Second State."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The northern hideout is over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.01,0:10:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and see Jugo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.37,0:10:10.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Hey! Wait, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.76,0:10:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Who is this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.47,0:10:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A male...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.73,0:10:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The next one I kill\Nwill be a guy, after all...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.77,0:10:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.23,0:10:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If the next one who comes\Nthrough that door is a woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.79,0:10:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.92,0:10:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The guards have all been killed...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and the prisoners have escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Then there's no way\Nwe can tell which one is Jugo...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:10:59.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Eh, Sasuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:03.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin, is Jugo among them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Cripes, what a pain!\NJust wait a bit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.69,0:11:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, he's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.92,0:11:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, I can fight without\Nworrying who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.77,0:11:26.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Just avoid killing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.37,0:11:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from the Hidden Leaf,\Nafter all...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.32,0:11:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You should've killed that\Nguy back there too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.50,0:11:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,So naïve...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.30,0:11:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:47.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay away! You all stink!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.51,0:12:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're strong... You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The keys!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.89,0:12:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.86,0:12:40.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Kill...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.01,0:13:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Karin, which way?\NLead the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!\NWhy're you ordering me around, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.64,0:13:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you just hurry and check?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.89,0:13:14.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the ability you\Npride yourself on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.11,0:13:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,That way!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.17,0:13:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, it's this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.07,0:13:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.01,0:13:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you lie? Suigetsu went...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.31,0:13:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Suigetsu has a big mouth,\Nthat's why I don't like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.68,0:13:48.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.39,0:13:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go... I can walk on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.23,0:14:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,So...the Curse Mark really does transform\Nthe body into such an ugly shape...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.67,0:14:04.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke, does your Curse Mark\Ndo the same to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.57,0:14:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke... Are you listening...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.13,0:14:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That bitch...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,A woman...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.94,0:14:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If a woman enters,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.81,0:14:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll kill her...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.14,0:14:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.65,0:14:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Jugo's inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.37,0:14:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,There...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.51,0:14:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Now then, which will it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.84,0:14:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! I'm gonna open it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:15:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go in first. Karin, stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.76,0:15:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.37,0:15:12.18,Default,,0,0,0,,It's gotta be a guy.\NIf it's a guy, I'll kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.10,0:15:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Bingo! I'm gonna kill!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.97,0:15:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.71,0:15:27.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? I'm back where I started.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I should've turned right back there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.99,0:15:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.03,0:15:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.71,0:15:41.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Just what is your purpose\Nin coming here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.37,0:15:46.84,Default,,0,0,0,,We came to take Jugo outta here,\Nso that he can join our team.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.84,0:15:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you guys realize...\Nwhat you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:16:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,If you let that guy...\Nout into the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.24,0:16:03.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I totally agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'll convince him...\Nwith force, if necessary.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.82,0:16:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You may be strong, but you're hardly...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.24,0:16:20.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen... If it weren't for Sasuke's words,\Nyou'd be dead right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.79,0:16:25.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Jugo will kill you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.97,0:16:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I really could care less\Nif one person died.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.24,0:16:35.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.94,0:16:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry!\NNaruto always gets so rowdy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.62,0:16:55.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Naruto, you idiot!\NSay you're sorry too!!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.73,0:16:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oww... Sakura that hurt!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.77,0:17:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,And? What did you want\Nto talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.79,0:17:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Mmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.07,0:17:11.43,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Granny Tsunade?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.43,0:17:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you have something\Nto talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.57,0:17:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,There's certain information that is\Nbeing spread throughout the region...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,It's about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Information?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.39,0:17:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,What? What about?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.24,0:17:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Orochimaru is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.04,0:17:38.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems Sasuke Uchiha killed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.77,0:17:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.17,0:17:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that...true?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.14,0:17:59.93,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake about it.\NI heard it from a reliable source.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.51,0:18:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Then...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.44,0:18:14.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Heh! After all, there's no way\Nhe'd get killed by Orochimaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That means Sasuke will be coming back\Nto the Hidden Leaf! Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.34,0:18:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That doesn't seem to be the case...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.51,0:18:37.99,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not over yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.28,0:18:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke's Chakra...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.21,0:19:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.81,0:19:19.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Not another copy of me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.60,0:19:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Sasuke...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.07,0:19:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But you're quite a guy to be able\N to do a Partial Transformation!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at controlling\Nyour Curse Mark!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.24,0:19:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no intention of fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.94,0:20:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I only wish to talk to you, Jugo.
